The 169.254.0.0 addresses are only used when DHCP server is not
available.

Address Bits
------------

-   8 bits = 256 addresses (254 hosts, minus the network and broadcast
    id\'s)
-   9 bits = 512 addresses
-   10 bits = 1024 addresses
-   11 bits = 2048 addresses

